room_title: Escape room "Operation Hotel" by The Safehouse Escape in Wichita
room_description: You work as a CIA operative, and will be traveling to London England and visiting the Hotel Thames on the hunt for a spy gone rogue by the name of Richard Werth. You have 60 minutes to find out where he is , but beware!  Werth has a love of tricks and traps; this case may not be so open and shut.
